.fi
.SH RETURN VALUE
.PP
Returns the arc tangent of \f[C]y\ /\ x\f[] in fixed point binary format
angle, from \-128 to 128.
If both \f[C]x\f[] and \f[C]y\f[] are zero, returns zero and sets
Allegro\[aq]s errno to EDOM.
